	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;I have a question that everyone seems to keep disagreeing over.... do necros need high or low CHA for better fears?  I get some people saying higher, some saying lower, but a lot of necro items are neg CHA so it would seem to me that lower is better.  Would someone who KNOWS post please and let me know?  Thanks,<br><br>Drakkonis<br>lvl 30 necro, brell server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
